If you want Enter the Gungeon for mobile, this game beats out Soul Knight by a mile. The presentation, gameplay, and progression are all handled excellently. You get a new experience with each of the 11 characters and difficulty modifiers that range from "oh this is a cool challenge" to "dear god why is this in the game this is horrible who would willingly do this to themselves." I would only ask for more content in the levels themselves. A few secret biomes/bosses to offer extra challenges.
